        "authorId" : "8be927c4-cfb4-4077-b355-f4f3d84849b8",
        "body" : "I'm not convinced we want the namespace controller to list/delete a resource in all the versions it appears. @derekwaynecarr, could that cause simultaneous deletions of the same resource via two different versions of an API group?\n",
        "createdAt" : "2016-11-14T22:41:14Z",
        "updatedAt" : "2016-11-18T22:32:24Z",
        "lastEditedBy" : "8be927c4-cfb4-4077-b355-f4f3d84849b8",
        "tags" : [
        ]
